cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with advanced computer vision techniques for generating whole face images from limited facial patches, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of deep learning networks and adversarial constraints also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the generation of realistic faces, which could fall under the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category. Finally, the use of image completion and generation techniques suggests a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
